KUfDUxF0V8w">Kỷ sự kỳ 01 - 紀事其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Kh%E1%BA%A3i-Si%C3%AAu/author-v6D2LCbIpae0gM4Dq3ytUA">Lương Khải Siêu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Th%E1%BA%ADn-Du%E1%BA%ADt/Ngh%C4%A9-b%E1%BA%A3n-th%C3%B4n-v%C3%A3n-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ti%C3%AAn-sinh/poem-2Xbod9AV0zR9HIhn2f0bcQ">Nghĩ bản thôn vãn Đông Dương tiên sinh - 擬本村挽東暘先生</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Th%E1%BA%ADn-Du%E1%BA%ADt/author-rOATA3YE3xI-b4gI-_iYag">Phạm Thận Duật</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A3n-%C4%90%C3%A0/T%E1%BA%BF-Chi%C3%AAu-Qu%C3%A2n/poem-xC8XM_Tv7EzGtySuzOxFAg">Tế Chiêu Quân - 祭昭君</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A3n-%C4%90%C3%A0/author-FOvItidPjMKModgAy49buw">Tản Đà</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/T%E1%BB%B1-t%E1%BA%BF-v%C4%83n/poem-eH6-j7g098C-j3cSVlJ0sg">Tự tế văn - 自祭文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-y4iJ6v3mYp-Z_KEorcHd_g">Đào Tiềm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Th%E1%BA%ADn-Du%E1%BA%ADt/V%C3%A3n-b%E1%BA%A3n-%E1%BA%A5p-b%C3%A0-ch%C3%A1nh/poem-gb-1271HVzFVBXdzzE1rDA">Vãn bản ấp bà chánh - 挽本邑婆正</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Th%E1%BA%ADn-Du%E1%BA%ADt/author-rOATA3YE3xI-b4gI-_iYag">Phạm Thận Duật</a>)<br></div>	</div>
